name: Azula
description: Second TI character. I'm having a lot of fun with this!

modelVersions.name: V1
modelVersions.description: Still testing things out. I'm using similar prompts but the style is little different than my Toph TI. Probably because of image choices. Not using show exclusive stuff for training.

meta.prompt: portrait, closeup, masterpiece, clean lines, girl, solo, Azula_Shurik-7000, western style art, blue fire light, located in a forest
